QuestData.Title: The Warchief Cometh
QuestData.Description: You're just in time, $nnub. It is $nnub, right?$B$B<Grand Executor Mortuus looks at a sheet of paper.>$B$BYes, that's what the paperwork says: "$nnub."$B$B<Grand Executor Mortuus points to your name on the sheet of paper.>$B$BWhere was I? Oh yes, you're just in time! The Warchief should be arriving at any moment to meet with our leader and savior, the Dark Lady herself. Just stand by and be at your best behavior. I expect that when this demonstration is over we will all receive commendations!
QuestData.LogDescription: Stand by for Warchief Garrosh Hellscream's arrival.
QuestData.RewardText: Well that was unexpected. I am not one to doubt our Warchief, but...$B$BNevermind! We have work to do. I'm sure the Dark Lady and the Warchief will get this all worked out.

Objectives.Objective: Stand by for Warchief Garrosh Hellscream's arrival
